held at 20:30 UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.
[LOG](../../../logs/2011/2011-07-13-log.txt).


## President's Report

Bdale reported that discussions were underway that were likely to result in at
least one resolution for a new associated project next month. He also commented
that DebConf11 was being held in Bosnia at the end of the month and a proposal
for an SPI BOF had been accepted.


