## Any other business

Bdale opened up the floor to our contributing members. MJ Ray congratulated us
on having produced an annual report and asked what plans continuing board
members had for SPI over the next year. Bdale indicated he'd like to get our
bylaws cleaned up. Jonathan mentioned some old website content that still
needed moved over. Joshua was continuing with plans for an SPI portion at
PgWest and also talking to various potential new projects. Jimmy pointed at his
position statement for the election. Finally Michael said he'd sent out a
reminder about a post-election membership purge of non-active members.

## Adjournment

The meeting was adjourned until Wednesday, August 10th, 2011 at 20:30
